## Features Needed for Quick Service Restaurants

- **Quick service ordering mode** — Designed for back-to-back transactions with minimal screen taps, fast modifier entry, and immediate order closure so the next customer can be served without delay.
- **Drive-thru ordering mode** — Supports continuous order flow from the menu board to the pickup window, keeping the kitchen synchronized with vehicle positions and estimated prep times.
- **Take-out ordering mode** — Handles advance orders, pickup scheduling, and packaging workflows so take-out doesn't disrupt counter operations.
- **Automatic combo recognition** — Detects when individual items qualify as a combo and applies the discount automatically, reducing cashier errors and speeding up the transaction.
- **Advanced Kitchen Display System (KDS)** — Routes orders to the correct prep stations with real-time visibility, displays preparation priority, and tracks order completion to maintain kitchen flow during high volume.
- **Integrated payment processing** — Processes card, contactless, and mobile payments directly within the POS to eliminate the delay of switching to a separate terminal.
- **Online ordering and delivery platform integration** — Connects with services like UberEats, Just Eat, and Deliverect through a built-in web connect system so off-premise orders enter the same kitchen queue.
- **Real-time inventory management** — Deducts stock as orders are placed, flags items approaching low thresholds, and helps prevent selling items that are out of stock.
- **Promotions management** — Enables operators to create, schedule, and track promotional offers in real time, including limited-time combos, discount codes, and loyalty-linked deals.
- **Gift cards and loyalty programs** — Supports customer retention through stored-value gift cards and loyalty point accumulation directly at the point of sale.
- **Balancing by POS terminal or by server** — Provides flexible reconciliation options at shift end, whether the operation tracks cash and transactions by individual terminal or by employee.
- **Custom reporting and analytics** — Delivers automatic reports on sales by daypart, average transaction value, item mix, labor efficiency, and promotional performance.

